    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 100.</p><p>Tier I: Regal Presence</p><p>Aura of Greatness. You emit an aura of commanding greatness in a 120-foot radius sphere centered on you. Friendly creatures that can see you within that radius can add your Charisma modifier to one ability check, attack roll, or saving throw. Once a creature has benefited from your Aura of Greatness, that creature cannot do so again until you finish a short or long rest.</p><p>Sovereign Will. Your spell save DC is increased by 1.</p></div>",
